bug.short_desc: Strikethroughs do not appear in CBSsports.com brackets

assigned_to.name: Nobody; OK to take it and work on it

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 524247 CBS Sports — no strikethroughs
When a chosen team fails to advance to the next round, the name of the team turns red, but a strikethrough does not appear through it, as it should (see attachments).

Created attachment 524248 CBS Sports — with strikethroughs
An example of how the strikethroughs should appear.
Which browser Version? Is this new or a regression? Please provide a link and STR.

(In reply to comment #2) > Which browser Version?
4.0
> Is this new or a regression?
New, as far as I can tell.
> Please provide a link and STR.
You can only see the problem if you register at cbssports.com and start a bracket. And since the tournament is over now, that probably isn't possible. I can give someone a link to my account to have a look, but I'd rather not do that in the bug.
